# PromptVault — Full Codebase Architecture Analysis

> Think of PromptVault like a **personal recipe book app** — except instead of recipes, people save **AI prompts**. They can organize them, share them with friends via a link, and even make a public portfolio of their best prompts for others to browse and "steal" into their own collection.

