## 2. Frontend — The Visual Layer (What Users See & Touch)

Your frontend is built with **React** (a popular tool for building interactive websites) and styled with **TailwindCSS** (a utility-based styling system). The visual style is intentionally **minimal, monospaced, developer-tool aesthetic** — lots of uppercase labels, tight tracking, and clean borders.

### Pages — 8 distinct screens

| Page | File | What it does |
|------|------|-------------|
| **Landing** | [Landing.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Landing.jsx) | Your personal prompt library. Shows all your prompts as clickable cards. Click = copy to clipboard. Has search and a "Public View" toggle (Creator-only). |
| **Admin** | [Admin.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Admin.jsx) | The "command center." Create new prompts, edit existing ones, delete with undo, search, and share vault links. The main management dashboard. |
| **Auth** | [Auth.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Auth.jsx) | Split-screen login/signup page. Supports email+password and Google OAuth. Has its own self-contained CSS (not Tailwind). |
| **Complete Profile** | [CompleteProfile.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/CompleteProfile.jsx) | One-time screen shown to Google OAuth users who don't have a username yet. Forces them to choose one before proceeding. |
| **Profile** | [Profile.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Profile.jsx) | Settings page: edit name, username (with live availability check), upload avatar, and — if on Creator plan — manage social links and public profile toggle. |
| **Shared Vault** | [SharedVault.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/SharedVault.jsx) | Someone else's full prompt collection viewed via a share link (`/vault/username`). Shows **ALL** prompts (public + private). Visitors can select prompts and add them to their own vault. |
| **Public Vault** | [PublicVault.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/PublicVault.jsx) | A creator's public portfolio (`/public/username`). Shows **only prompts marked as public**. Includes their social links and avatar. Visitors can bulk-add prompts. |
| **Verified** | [Verified.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Verified.jsx) | A simple landing page shown after email verification confirms the account. Redirects to home. |

