## 6. Data Flow — Step-by-Step Walkthroughs

### Flow A: "User creates a new prompt"

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant AF as AdminPromptForm
    participant RQ as React Query
    participant PS as promptService.createPrompt
    participant SB as Supabase DB

    U->>AF: Fills in name, body, tags, clicks "Save"
    AF->>PS: createPrompt({ name, body, tags, is_public })
    PS->>SB: supabase.auth.getUser() — verify identity
    SB-->>PS: Returns authenticated user
    PS->>SB: supabase.from('prompts').insert({...}).select().single()
    SB-->>PS: Returns new prompt row
    PS-->>AF: Returns prompt object
    AF->>RQ: Optimistically adds to cache + invalidates queries
    RQ-->>U: UI instantly shows the new prompt
```

### Flow B: "User copies a prompt from their vault"

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant PC as PromptCard
    participant CB as Clipboard API
    participant PS as promptService.incrementUsage
    participant SB as Supabase DB

    U->>PC: Clicks a prompt card
    PC->>CB: navigator.clipboard.writeText(prompt.body)
    CB-->>PC: ✓ Copied
    PC-->>U: Shows "Copied to clipboard" overlay
    PC->>PS: incrementUsage(prompt.id)
    PS->>SB: Fetch current usage_count, then UPDATE +1
    SB-->>PS: Updated row
    Note over PC: Also optimistically updates React Query cache
```

### Flow C: "Visitor adds prompts from someone's Public Vault"

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Visitor
    participant PV as PublicVault Page
    participant PS as promptService.addPromptToVault
    participant SB as Supabase DB

    V->>PV: Clicks "Add Prompts to Your Vault"
    PV-->>V: Enters selection mode → checkboxes appear
    V->>PV: Selects 3 prompts, clicks "Add 3 Prompts"
    PV->>PS: For each selected prompt → addPromptToVault(prompt)
    PS->>SB: Check for duplicates (source_prompt_id or name+body match)
    SB-->>PS: No duplicates found
    PS->>SB: INSERT new prompt (is_public: false, source_prompt_id, attribution_username)
    SB-->>PS: Success
    PS-->>PV: { success: true }
    PV-->>V: Shows "Prompts Added!" confirmation
```

### Flow D: "New Google user signs up"

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant Auth as Auth Page
    participant SB as Supabase Auth
    participant AC as AuthContext
    participant AS as authService
    participant DB as profiles table
    participant CP as CompleteProfile

    U->>Auth: Clicks "Continue with Google"
    Auth->>SB: supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth({ provider: 'google' })
    SB-->>U: Redirects to Google → user authorizes → redirects back
    SB->>AC: onAuthStateChange fires with session
    AC->>AS: handleAuthenticatedUser → ensureProfile(user)
    AS->>DB: SELECT * FROM profiles WHERE id = user.id
    DB-->>AS: No profile found (PGRST116)
    AS->>DB: INSERT new profile (username: null, plan: 'FREE')
    DB-->>AS: Returns new profile
    AS-->>AC: Profile has username === null
    AC->>CP: Redirect to /complete-profile
    CP-->>U: Shows "Choose your username" form
    U->>CP: Enters username, clicks Continue
    CP->>AS: updateProfile(userId, { username, full_name })
    AS->>DB: UPDATE profiles SET username = '...'
    CP-->>U: Hard redirect to /admin via window.location.href
```

